      publishedAt: "2021-11-06T10:14:36Z",
      content:
        "Consider 5 November 2021 as day one. Not merely three years since Azeem Rafiq first made allegations of racism and bullying at Yorkshire, approaching the club with his grievances that initially went … [+7026 chars]",
